 enjoy this tile matching game whenever and wherever you like - without Wi-Fi.\nOffline Games: Enjoy the Blossom Match tile game anywhere, anytime with our offline mode - Perfect for puzzling on the go.\n10,000+ Tile Game Levels: From relaxing starter rounds to tricky brain-benders, Blossom Match has something for everyone. Keep advancing, matching tiles across different worlds and see if you can become the ultimate matching games champion.\nHow to Play\nTap and match tiles in groups of three to remove them from the board.\nClear all tiles to win the round.\nProgress through levels that grow more challenging, keeping the fun fresh.\nWhether you‚Äôre looking for a fun tile game to pass the time, a relaxing escape after a long day, or a mental workout from matching games for adults, Blossom Match is here to deliver.\nDownload Blossom Match‚Äôs Triple Match Puzzle today and join the ultimate matching tiles adventure. Relax, and conquer levels in your new favourite matching games', 'Unwind and relax with tile-matching puzzles and brain games', NULL, '["https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/m3XVWqONvuzEYfrdfWHAOFYg9UnFKLbZKVcmDjdgg0CP6nzjdch8rqEwfkb365PlTQ=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/cBkTdnrgns25cw9r4Zg3NsznLHrw9YH5vWDa29F7UTtHkkfjcQxUoADaQuIPXMy0iV0=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/kcwO2lfGR5YAIlx9sG33_KBHyf9_nPplOlGt3_gCPb0VhBt_7uBCVQNQ1XBPvmiseNpt1jVzUH1Oq2XCVa55=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/6Dq4V9OSvbFOpXMa5MiVLSO65lt6wfw9890W00TYGl0qakqlXLzXsY2OQKOZxM8_RA=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/iy9_Bt6pmfwwXXH51W89cYdOfvoZcfmeLaiv7hbGgPEKXTAooOYegSwXWpsCTvYXX_g=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/7K6nBteoYF1TEUlWXmnRcN4KHi8-o11a2dqQ0O4uwcTsCO6yPFDAwSwYP0f7Wv-6bhQ=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/E5ljeuLj4VifdY9oyDNI6LjIC6IymTqpS7gpAnxMIjO2Q6DfcxyerJpWn88BeagMpWE=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/5UI69ni48nwPM-fQ2HnQfgbPJdw4r28wqB-