  ('cml1au3sy000px93x14j6qke8', 'Bubble Shooter: Bubble Pop', 'com.dopuz.panda.saga', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dopuz.panda.saga', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/BC2GpSm_Xq_xygyG1Sme5sz8M4tcIuZYVnh3fz7hhcLiDNffzscus4RdXcnWHvsPVCgE=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/com.dopuz.panda.saga-icon__hHeh6GQR.jpg', 'cml1au3e70006x93xh8m634ny', '[]', '4.3', '75.6K reviews', '75.6K reviews', NULL, 'Bubble Shooter: Bubble Pop, an exciting casual game adventure with your vidmate where you can create bubble pop as a bubble buster will begin! In bubble shooter games, you need to shoot bubble or bump pop at over 300 captivating babble blast levels to bring bubble pop offline games.\nIn bubble shooter offline games , shoot bubble to relax in casual games and win babble strike levels with a vidmate, enjoy the match 3 gaming experience in bubble shooter games and discover the endless Bubble Popping Fun in bubble shooter offline games!\nJoin the bubble pop journey! Once you start playing bubble shooter games to shoot bubble and bump pop, you simply won‚Äôt put it down! You will easily achieve your bubble pop dream via bump pop for bubble buzz in bubble games!\nBubble Shooter: Bubble Pop Game Features:\n‚≠êÔ∏è Classic babble puzzle games, brand shoot bubble gameplay\n‚≠êÔ∏è 300 fun levels of bubble mania, infinite challenge\n‚≠êÔ∏è Accurate aiming vidmate controls, fluent bubble matching\n‚≠êÔ∏è Shoot bubble with power-up balls, get higher score\n‚≠êÔ∏è Rescue cute pet, little animals are waiting for rescued\n‚≠êÔ∏è Easy to pick up, train your vidmate, brain and finger\n‚≠êÔ∏è Daily challenge bubble pop offline games,  get game props\n‚≠êÔ∏è Enchanting graphic and bubble crush special effects\nHow to play bubble pop games well?\nüåü Tap and move the laser, aim, shoot & pop bubbles!\nüåü Pop 3 or more color bubble combos to make babble burst\nüåü Clear all the bubbles to level up, create a bubble legend\nüåü Less moves pass a bubble lev