  ('cml1au3t2002zx93xmcyjm16s', 'Timelie', 'com.snapbreak.timelie', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.snapbreak.timelie', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Ia8HFid_HxiqMaiqght-q4fMAwaELQMu78a_8HlDsk8k4IzP4mb6nPswZlM3r-PNbfM=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/com.snapbreak.timelie-icon_yx3TKtSiju.jpg', 'cml1au3hl0009x93xl5rsq9f7', '[]', '4.6', '8.44K reviews', '8.44K reviews', NULL, '*TRY BEFORE YOU BUY - NO ADS!*\nTimelie is a stealth puzzle adventure where you control time like a media player. This stealth puzzle adventure offers unique challenges that will test your problem-solving skills. Experience the thrill of puzzle-solving and the excitement of stealth gameplay as you perceive future events to plan your escape strategy in this captivating adventure. Sneak past enemies, solve intricate puzzles, and manipulate time through a unique adventure with a mysterious cat and a little girl with precognitive powers.\nFeatures:\n- Play Act 1 for free and get a taste of the thrilling stealth puzzle adventure.\n- Control time like a media player: pause, rewind, and fast-forward to overcome challenges.\n- Play as both the girl and the cat, each with unique abilities that complement each other.\n- Experience a vibrant and surreal world filled with challenging puzzles and exciting escapes.\n- Enjoy the cat''s hilarious antics‚Äîsometimes it''s helpful, sometimes it''s just being a cat!\nEvery second matters in Timelie. Perceive future events to plan your escape strategy from the past, solve challenging puzzles, sneak around enemies, and manipulate time throughout this thrilling adventure of companionship and stealth.\nThe Timeline ability gives players the power to control time just like a media player. Drag the Timeline left to rewind time and undo your past mistakes. Drag it right to see the future unfold, giving you valuable information to change the past. This unique ability adds a new layer to the puzzle and stealth elements, making e