  ('cml1au434004qx93xo0rj08aa', 'Battle Cars: Nitro PvP Shooter', 'com.tinybytes.massivecars', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tinybytes.massivecars', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/wgmezSyFjj7V6XJdwZrEaa9qIAJrGRW-PBSMOPobGOd5KiSpDbjN-kiKfhmnCjdIvpO8=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/com.tinybytes.massivecars-icon_G96N-T1P3.jpg', 'cml1au37f0000x93xcjfk9gjy', '[]', '3.7', '23.2K reviews', '23.2K reviews', NULL, 'Where speed meets destruction. Drive fast, shoot faster. Race, fight, win!\nThis is more than just a racing or fighting game. It''s Battle Cars, a car realtime competitive multiplayer shooter where your skills behind the wheel and in combat are put to the ultimate test in a cyberpunk post-apocalyptic MOBA action game with a unique 3D graphic style.\nAwarded an honorable mention in the Pocket Gamer Awards 2025.\nRoar the engine and get ready for a high-octane brawl in Battle Cars! Dive into intense gameplay against Fury machines crafted by players from around the globe and compete in thrilling PVP car combat. The better you assemble it, the more fights you will win.\nBattle Cars awaits! Upgrade, and rule the rage in the battlefield. Be the best driver, control the streets with your mad fury. Crush the war game, cross out enemies, make the wheels burn, don''t stop accelerating until fire is burning in your exhaust pipe, wreck their cars into twisted metal, and claim the title of King of the Road.\n| FEATURES |\nDIVERSE CAR LINEUP\nWith 15+ unique customizable cars, and over 12 guns & 12 collision / melee weapons, you''re ready to combine them to conquer any scenario. Enhance your favorites and customize them with a lot of patterns, camouflage, and decals to become a legend in the PvP arena!  Fill your garage with brawl vehicles like buggy, armored vehicles, cyber trucks, sports racing cars and monster trucks. Don''t cross out or discard any of them, you‚Äôll need all of them to dominate! The gameplay is as hot as the wheels.\nSPECIAL CAR ABILITIES\nEquip your car with FPS weapons, machine guns, missiles, sniper rifles, rocket launchers, and flamethrowers for extreme fun and intense vehicle combat. Car abilities are key to gaining the upper hand and eliminating your enemies, blitz them all to become the best Vigilante.\nVARIED 4v4 PvP MODES\nEach mode demands different strategies and skills, catering to experienced players. Free-For-All offers unpredictability, while 4v4 battles focus on team dynamics. Capture the Flag requires strategy, and Domination demands coordination. Modes unlock gradually, providing new challenges in diverse Battle Royale arenas. Quick matchmaking and under-five-minute battles ensure fast-paced action for every preference.\nUNIQUE MAPS\nBattle across varied environments, from neon-lit cities to desert roads and futuristic arenas. Each map demands specific tactics, pushing you to adapt and conquer. Navigate a dystopian cyber metropolis, avoid traps, and use the terrain to your advantage. Take jump runs for spectacular twists and aerial maneuvers. Are you ready to survive in a battlefield full of explosions, crossfire, and cars crashing?\nALLIANCES AND ALLIANCE WARS\nTeam with your friends, join forces in squad, and engage in thrilling Alliance Wars. Form gangs and become a road warrior in this epic car warfare. Participate in gang wars, distribute the roles Speedsters, Attackers, Suppliers, Tanks, Defenders and crush your rivals with your warlord tactics. Build strategies in intense team battles and rise to lead league leaderboards.\nINTUITIVE CONTROLS\nEnjoy smooth drive & FPS-inspired controls tailored for Max competitive PvP epic combats and customize your setup to suit your play style. Execute perfect maneuvers and dominate the war zone with ease.\nPLAY ANYWHERE\nBattle Cars is optimized for most 4G/LTE networks, allowing for seamless play on the go. With quick matches, it''s perfect for players looking for fast-paced automobile combat.\nJoin the paradi