  ('cml1au434004sx93xju4uhvkn', 'Ninja Party: Team Up & Brawl', 'com.nekki.ninjaparty', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nekki.ninjaparty', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/tTTBswQytYRaR-D2jWU1q_-K7oVtSmenhqrDoAwtnS3jEDov5sXQtdW5gHD1doY9mw=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/com.nekki.ninjaparty-icon_wHULcYwlhD.jpg', 'cml1au37f0000x93xcjfk9gjy', '[]', '4.4', '6.62K reviews', '6.62K reviews', NULL, 'Ninja Party is a free parkour multiplayer action game from the creators of Shadow Fight and Vector. Compete with other players online in fun challenges for the title of the best ninja!\nMULTIPLAYER PARKOUR ACTION\nRun on walls, catch up with opponents and deal with them like a real ninja: using katanas, kunai, hammers, and anything that comes to hand ‚Äî even a frying pan. This is Ninja Party, where each round is full of unpredictable fighting chaos. Did you fail and get knocked out? No problem ‚Äî immediately return to the game and punish the offender, no boring waiting! Dynamic multiplayer gameplay guarantees that every match feels fresh and fast-paced. Whether you‚Äôre new or experienced, there‚Äôs always a way to surprise your opponents in this multiplayer battle.\nPARTY ROYALE ‚Äî BECOME THE BEST NINJA\nRemain the only one among up to 12 players competing for the title of the best ninja. Complete challenges in various game modes one by one ‚Äî experience the true ninja party royale! As each stage progresses, players are eliminated, and in the end, there is only one winner. Victory requires speed, cunning, and adaptability ‚Äî every move counts in this online showdown. Welcome to the world of real-time multiplayer fighting games, where chaos meets strategy.\nTEAM UP WITH FRIENDS\nTeam up with friends or meet new allies online! Create a group of up to three ninjas and lead your clan to victory. Working together gives you a real edge: cover each other, set traps, and turn the tide of battle. Playing as a team makes every moment of Ninja Party even more exciting ‚Äî and unpredictable. Show your loyalty or go full betrayal ‚Äî it‚Äôs up to you.\nCOLLECT AND UPGRADE SKINS\nJust play and replenish your collection of unique ninja skins. Win matches, complete challenges, and unlock new appearances. Customize your style and stand out among other players ‚Äî from classic stealthy looks to wild, fun costumes. As you progress, you can upgrade your favorite skins and improve their appearance by reaching new levels. Your ninja, your style.\nNinja Party is not just a game ‚Äî it‚Äôs a nonstop action-packed experience with wild parkour, chaotic battles, and fast multiplayer rounds that keep you coming back. With up to 12 players online, a variety of game modes, and tons of unlockables, this game has everything for fans of multiplayer action games, fighting games, and party chaos. Play solo or with friends, take part in the most unpredictable competition, and become the ultimate ninja legend!\nReady for the party? Jump into the Ninja Party ‚Äî your next multiplayer battle awaits.', 'Parkour action from the authors of Shadow Fight & Vector. Fun 12-player PvP game', NULL, '["https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/etd7rwnunlOdOybKId9pQ7C6m46eCAuxBt5K1jaqS5wq_Q9zZbHrsgUMz6zhwT9urWs=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/KXqAZHgKGjwE2R7dAqzWeq7zmNBloaRUejUWAMGrrgybcifR2Md_BTyJkTn4RrD49tI=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/XrV4hMQIclGmur-dvJAhgRnJmn6YDhFByBnq9oJ9N1vzk6kWKrchYLb7kTYOwQi974g=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Cqs2KUgURdP3F1Rd_CZYrL57iiOytgSp0Owpiu-0IAONCz31OqK8UQd56xky5JtpBf8=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/D9XGNxDpEo4rQBoxz8vOIA4uE4bzbwIzrQn7h_3o5FrXDg9FC_M8-ai5XmNyTCJxty4=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/5BLURX06m9-d-0KsCL4mi1Y8bXMKxhpRCzSZokXN6Y_ra8MsgjpLzSq1dXxXsIuEbnk=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/C-2axF0h0N6UMQYLa6xfvyLz-WEpwGiUPBYlTaa10VGbbE1SrTfjIRhk1sPavdKlB-k=w526-h296-rw","http