  ('cml1au434004lx93xn2b22mbw', 'ScarFall 2.0 : Battle Royale', 'xsquads.scarfall.battleroyalegame', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=xsquads.scarfall.battleroyalegame', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/0-Y5rFd3X4MJhMuH5OrS-_B3lTiJDH5iI-sMW2yDUcfKdw5P1pS5qyE52k4Z79BQf5Uf=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/xsquads.scarfall.battleroyalegame-icon_LAm9S6a89.jpg', 'cml1au37f0000x93xcjfk9gjy', '[]', '4.4', '53.6K reviews', '53.6K reviews', NULL, 'ScarFall 2.0 is a feature-rich Made in India battle royale game crafted for gamers who enjoy real-time combat, squad-based strategy, and fast-paced shooting experiences. Combining the depth of an online action game with the thrill of a multiplayer action game, it offers a unique mix of survival gameplay, voice chat teamwork, and intense PvP encounters set in iconic Indian locations.\nSeason 03: ScarPass ‚Äì Kaal Reborn\nEnter the underworld and awaken your dark legacy. Season 03 brings a hell-themed ScarPass packed with infernal outfits, blazing weapon skins, and exclusive rewards inspired by fire, shadows, and rebellion. Rise through the chaos, dominate the arena, and prove you are the true Kaal of the battleground.\nWhether you''re new to action shooting games or an experienced squad leader, ScarFall 2.0 battle royale game provides the right balance of challenge and fun. Play solo or team up with friends for exciting matches across varied game modes and battlegrounds. So what are you waiting for? Pre-register now for exclusive rewards! Don''t miss out on these limited-time benefits.\nGame Modes for Every Type of Player:\nClassic Mode (Andaman Map) ‚Äì 40-player lobbies with 3 respawn chances. A dynamic mode for reviving, regrouping, and winning as a team.\nSurvival Mode (Mumbai Map) ‚Äì A tough 100-player match with no respawns. Navigate high-rise zones, close alleys, and travel using moving local trains to reach strategic locations.\nTeam Deathmatch (TDM) ‚Äì Choose between quick 4v4 skirmishes in Snow Park or large-scale 8v8 action in Goa. Perfect for fast-paced team fights.\nExplore Unique Indian Battlegrounds:\nMumbai ‚Äì Urban warfare across stations, rooftops, and local trains that connect key areas of the map.\nAndaman ‚Äì Island-style open terrain ideal for wide-spread shootouts.\nGoa ‚Äì A scenic town converted into an 8v8 multiplayer warzone.\nSnow Park ‚Äì A close-range frozen arena designed for 4v4 action.\nFrom tropical beaches to icy parks and crowded train platforms ‚Äî ScarFall 2.0 brings diverse Indian battlegrounds to life.\nCore Features That Define the Experience:\nPlay in real-time with players across India in a smooth online multiplayer game.\nA multiplayer game that rewards coordination, reflexes, and smart movement.\nTalk and strategize using live voice chat in the lobby and during matches.\nChoose your favorite guns and build custom loadouts for relevant modes.\nUnlock exclusive gun skins, outfits, and rewards with the ScarPass.\nDrive Indian-style vehicles including chakdo, rickshaw, jeep, bike, car and helicopter.\nUse local trains in Mumbai to reposition across the map.\nCompete in ranked matches and climb up the leaderboard.\nEnjoy flexible team options: solo, duo, or squad.\nMade for Online Game Lovers:\nIf you‚Äôre looking for a true Indian game that combines shooting, survival, and real multiplayer action ‚Äî ScarFall 2.0 delivers. Whether you prefer TDM, large-scale squad battles, or simply exploring Indian environments with friends, this adventure game gives you the freedom to play your way.\nRuns Smooth on Most Phones:\nScarFall 2.0 battle royale is carefully optimized to deliver smooth performance across a wide range of devices ‚Äî from entry-level phones to high-end smartphones. Players can enjoy responsive controls, stable frame rates, and immersive visuals without compromise.\nReal Game Feel, Real Team Play:\nScarFall 2.0 captures the essence of online shooting games ‚Äî from smart movement and map control to clutch