  ('cml1au435004zx93xx82xf9wo', 'Zombastic: Survival game', 'com.playmotional.survival', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.playmotional.survival', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/S2elLEZk8g7rnSCrEerIaa4ffTua-Q0XX7yjgnPBI7UmttV7K7-NaahMpBx8JOT4wqg=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/com.playmotional.survival-icon_1v0WxvoTL.jpg', 'cml1au37f0000x93xcjfk9gjy', '[]', '4.4', '40.9K reviews', '40.9K reviews', NULL, 'Step into a world overrun by the undead in the ultimate survival shooter, Zombastic: Survival Game. You assume the role of a resourceful hero trapped inside a once-bustling supermarket, now crawling with hordes of ravenous zombies. What was once a safe haven for shoppers has become a nightmare, with every aisle and corner harboring danger. Your mission is simple yet daunting‚Äîsurvive.\nSurvival won‚Äôt be easy. Supplies are scarce, weapons are makeshift, and there‚Äôs no help coming. To make it out alive, you‚Äôll need to scavenge for whatever you can find. Whether it‚Äôs food to sustain yourself, materials to craft weapons, or tools to unlock hidden areas, every item you collect brings you one step closer to survival.\nUnlock Powerful Abilities and Weapons\nAs you progress, your hero will become stronger, unlocking new abilities and discovering powerful weapons to help you in your fight for survival. From crafting more advanced firearms to mastering combat techniques that give you the edge in battle, every new skill and weapon brings you closer to escaping the supermarket alive.\nThe more zombies you kill, the more experience you gain‚Äîunlocking powerful upgrades that will turn the tide in your favor. But beware‚Äîthe zombies get tougher too. As you delve deeper into the game, new types of enemies emerge, each more dangerous and cunning than the last.\nFace Terrifying Bosses\nThe undead aren‚Äôt your only enemies. Zombie bosses lurk in the shadows, more powerful and terrifying than the rest. These nightmarish creatures r