  ('cml1au4aj006fx93xk925mirw', 'Standoff 2', 'com.axlebolt.standoff2', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.axlebolt.standoff2', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/VpUP8AqSRB-R_uusCh1jeQLa2LRyqPB3Vb_9tY9O8Y-2wzJvtwwrZWWhP0xxTuFf5bpz-DP6LrdcYOc-KjIdOA=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/com.axlebolt.standoff2-icon_9hjjJCt8v.jpg', 'cml1au37f0000x93xcjfk9gjy', '[]', '4.3', '11.7M reviews', '11.7M reviews', NULL, 'Standoff 2 is a free-to-play first-person action shooter with over 300 million installs worldwide. Immerse yourself in the engaging world of tactical battles and dynamic firefights in the free-to-play multiplayer shooter genre.\nEXPLORE A DETAILED ENVIRONMENT\nEmbark on a global journey across extremely detailed maps ‚Äî from the picturesque mountains of Province to the deserted streets of Sandstone. Each location in Standoff 2 offers a unique setting for engaging confrontations.\nTAKE PART IN REALISTIC SHOOTOUTS\nExperience a fully immersive and realistic battle in an online shooter. Shoot a variety of firearms, including AWM and M40 sniper rifles, Deagle and USP pistols, and the iconic AKR and P90. The recoil and spread of the guns are unique, making gunfights feel as though they were real. The diverse arsenal offers more than 25 weapons. Choose your gun. You can use everything right from the start ‚Äî there''s no need to level up to unlock weapons.\nTEAM UP WITH YOUR FRIENDS IN COMPETITIVE MATCHES\nBattle opponents in matches where you rank is at stake. Start off with the calibration at the beginning of the Season and rank up to get unique rewards.\nONLY SKILLS SHAPE SUCCESS\nDive into a fully skill-based gameplay where your abilities and tactics matter the most. Forget about casual shooters ‚Äî here it''s all about teamwork and personal skills. Responsive controls and flexible settings make Standoff 2 one of the best games among online shooters.\nCUSTOMIZE YOUR ARSENAL WITH SKINS AND STICKERS\nPersonalize your weapons with an extensive selection of skins, stickers, and charms. Create a bold and unique design that reflects your style and make your arsenal truly unique. Claim Battle Pass rewards in regular updates, get skins from cases and boxes, and your collection will surely be the most impressive one.\nDIFFERENT GAME MODES FOR ENDLESS ACTION\nChoose from a variety of game modes: 5v5 fights, Allies: 2v2 confrontations, or deadly 1v1 duels. Have fun in Free-for-all or Team Deathmatch, Tactical fights or endless shootouts, duels or special themed modes.\nDOMINATE IN CLAN BATTLES\nForm alliances and win battles together with your clan. Team up with your friends to achieve glory on the battlefield.\nREALISTIC GRAPHICS\nDive into intense online battles with advanced 3D graphics and animations. The shooter supports 120 FPS, providing a smooth immersive gameplay experience on your mobile device.\nREGULAR UPDATES AND SEASONS.\nThere''s never a dull moment in Standoff 2 thanks to regular updates. They''re all about new mechanics, unique skin collections, engaging maps, and new modes. Experience a festive atmosphere by checking out updates dedicated to New Year and Halloween that offer exclusive content, holiday challenges, and limited edition skins.\nJOIN THE COMMUNITY\nDon''t miss the opportunity to enjoy the action ‚Äî download Standoff 2 and become a part of the world gaming community! Communicate with players on social media and stay up to date with the latest events:\nFacebook: https://facebook.com/Standoff2Official\nYoutube: https://www.youtube.com/@Standoff2Game\nDiscord: https://discord.gg/standoff2\nTikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@standoff2_en\nNeed help or have questions? Visit our tech support site: https://help.standoff2.com/en/\nEngage in epic battles, show off your skills, and dominate the Standoff 2 arena!', 'Take action in renewed Standoff in the form of a dynamic FPS!', NULL, '["https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/2T8FMzzlUDRAMmmyHifP2SCz_H6jrfh-qCg3I4S24a5ic0cMipmM-gEtg27B