  ('cml1au4h200abx93xka6x603y', 'Nightfall: Kingdom Frontier TD', 'com.fansipan.nightfall.tower.simulation.strategy.td.game', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fansipan.nightfall.tower.simulation.strategy.td.game', 'https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/K4-f3RaKNOc-YICu47fN-XpAYnJQjcGcIJ73gho29Fu_2znI54xpZHBm4L2bAEXfw7Q=s256-rw', 'https://ik.imagekit.io/yk0evs8op/games/com.fansipan.nightfall.tower.simulation.strategy.td.game-icon_p2GGW0l2zP.jpg', 'cml1au3mz000ex93x0yghfg2i', '[]', '4.7', '71.3K reviews', '71.3K reviews', NULL, 'üéÅüî• Gift codes:\nNIGHTFALL8888\nImmerse yourself in a tactical and epic tower defense adventure, where you showcase your strategy of tower defense and resource management to build, battle, and conquer in a medieval RPG fantasy.\nüè∞ Step into a cursed land: Once upon a time, in a faraway realm, there lived Lord James VII, who ruled a kingdom cursed for an eternal war. As night falls, savage creatures spawn from the darkness every night. It''s your mission to defend the kingdom and lead Lord James VII on a bold quest to battle against hordes and conquer the lands.\n‚öîÔ∏è Daytime preparation, nighttime warfare: By day, Lord James VII is a master strategist, constructing fortresses, upgrading defenses, and recruiting legendary heroes. But when night falls and the war begins, he transforms into a fearless warrior, leading his troops in epic survival battles.\nüëë A story yet to be written: Will Lord James VII survive the war and succeed in his quest? That, my friend, is a story yet to be written. Your strategy, leadership, and courage will decide his quest. Your defense strategy should be strong enough to defeat the endless waves of hordes in his quest for a glorious victory.\nüí• KEY FEATURES:\nPREPARE BY DAY, DEFEND BY NIGHT\nA dynamic rhythm of building by day and defending by night! Build and strengthen your perfect defense and army from a combination of powerful troops and awesome towers by day, and fight for an intense survival war when night falls to protect the kingdom from horde attacks. Command the best defense strategy as you clash on the battlefield!\nRESOURCE MANAGEMENT\nYou actively control your resources by building gold generating houses or farms along with defense towers and troops to protect your base and upgrade them later on. You must balance limited resources between economy and defense, adding a layer of resource management rarely seen in classic TD games. Master the principles of resource management to maximize your chances of survival.\nPREPARATION PHASE BEFORE COMBAT\nPlace and upgrade all economy and defense construction before the battle begins. You cannot build or upgrade them once you are in combat. Summon cards to choose the perfect tactical support for each battlefield. Defense towers are placed around your castle to defend your base realm by automatically attacking enemies when they are close. Upgrade your towers for increased strength, damage, range, or special effects.\nDIVERSIFIED CONTENT\nConquer 4 World Maps. Join the Adventure and Daily Challenge. Unite with other players to defeat the ultimate boss in the Guild System. Showcase your power and strategy in PvP battles (coming soon). Stay tuned for seasonal events and enjoy hidden treasure surprises. Customize your own kingdom with various divine, demonic, and mystical civilizations.\nMOVABLE HEROES WITH ACTIVE SKILLS\nYou control your hero with active abilities and movement, blending TD with light action RPG elements. Join the lucky draw and open lucky chests to unlock legendary heroes and ultimate weapons that can buff your hero''s combat power. Experience the thrill of running and shooting  as you fight against enemies and defend your castle at the same time. Level up your archer and swordsman troops to create an unstoppable army and gain more tactical power in battle!\nEPIC OFFLINE TOWER DEFENSE GAME\nExtra offline TD game modes to push your tower defense strategy to the limit. Play offline anywhere as the adventure doesn‚Äôt stop even if the internet does. Enjoy epic tower defense missions and hours of fun strategic battles anytime, anywhere!\nIt''s a real role-playing adventure! Are you ready for this epic tower defense strategy game?', 'Epic Strategy Game: Tower Defense RPG', NULL, '["https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/tDTUG9uLEupWvPNg1lJyXvh3KOKiLWkjTW7fXjC41S7UHkLEAtjNqW6Ql148ke-MZA=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/GEZh2jVeHQ818XatQjuYejoNLemAJhwy4Jw_nHqSny-9Qfcmiey3O2TZHzIsjIbGbEE=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/VerEMqMiXw1TiM8vPLqu8VfNDj_kVliHH09LCN5KVdPI37hEaBo-NRYPblndMc7ewuk=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/FK7sGiSV_J2bHbbKNx4TshNaMlkw0USdmn84aWHnFiHhYG-3zl0Ekxi3FCYcQCODNfA=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/ZgMjHVWRxHyurcXlyFkixZ_m6VuFd3azhpI2CRqpe1t0SFrwIpjBtSDjCgzkYlQNsQ=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/f3Woen17RvE1mqIixFm47WYp5gytI9ibgwaZ2TDW1Lq9vTceXCSz1fyaITwxiYqTzDA=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/KaZ0v7HLWXzVEHplS0YcLVUxtEgRqpNFiu9VJu07qP82POR8oSr8YwnhOOvdTRtC2g=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/RR4BW6lyeWp5uvKj-J53dKPJJiqlWm1_lV8_B_7WIPqtGrTYPSukpyGHEZAzj4MW5g=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/y6QfBHJEVRqZY0jO6KTcZI_tRAHDt1pIcfty1RzQY8P6NUrTcK_t1_zcVlS-x7HGxYyL=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/8DjkbgGrfXh0umYNRVOO4MgsMUVxdLec8Pqv5xKPiGM1wef3818L8pj8fk6S_w69oPbX=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/ZLaLuu_tNlwM-1UIERCtvJtpfgCS3zDw8BiOgJlDxuh9dRuzgY8dXy4lkpf9UJ7eVHFP=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/-lbOPeFC2eORj_VQ8JGVHxLQNXYQtwhFV5JfCzKNeJvmXLQv4vVCEWEtUzctsgB8ZnM=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/KFJ20SlIpPKQd2pOCcL5cLemGA54h7A-4gmZwNluZQWn9gWip8l6v7ZSzo8mOZfoNnpl=w526-h296-rw","https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/4FglsaoDgRI5MrMvn4KVuM3ynxFL1GJn9uDWZj_6ROAZs-XsCNWtIqxIx7ZpyA2EWS4=w526-h296-rw","http